attributeList.attribute: This set represents a merge between the AI-1MAIN and AI-1REPEAT to give AI-1, with proteins remapped from the nucleotide sequence identifier to the corresponding UniProtKB protein identifier.

Bait and prey proteins were co-expressed using the TNT SP6 Coupled Wheat Germ Extract System. Expressed proteins in wheat germ extract were added to glutathione-Stransferase detection plates, washed, and and subsequently incubated with mouse anti-HA monoclonal antibody followed by anti-mouse HRP-coupled secondary antibody for visualisation.
